</p>
<p>
<seg id="50">He can say: "We change the law and allow it", but he cannot say that we will do as if not at all.</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id="51">In the law on the public awarding, the regulation is quite strict as for the way in which it is necessary to act formally. And this way it is like a debit to be to protect the public competition.</seg>
<seg id="52">But, on the other hand, he is a tragic actor who excludes the candidate with the best offer for not fulfilling the formal requirements.</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id="53">The law will never be perfect, but its application must be correct. This is, in my opinion, what we lack.</seg>
</p>
